data.description: EXCEPTIONAL 3/2 + den POOL home in desirable Country Club Estates. Generac 2200k whole home generator - no more power losses during storms or outages! The whole home generator has a buried 500-gallon tank! There is a solar pool heater for those cooler evenings. Enjoy sitting on your lanai and watching the wildlife near the canal. The lanai has access from 4 separate sliders; also via the guest bathroom. This gorgeous canal front property also boasts several fruit trees with plenty of room to add more.  An 8x10 shed is there for all your yard and garden needs. Schedule your showing today!
